title: Subject.13.Update.v1.2-BAT
description:
Subject 13 - Update 1.2

Thanks for your precious feedbacks who helped detecting and fixing issues. Mac users should be able to play without problem now.
In addition, we are happy to offer 2 original soundtracks of the game composed by Olivier Deriviere to everyone.

Update contents:


Added:
2 Subject 13 Soundtracks now available for free!

Fixed:
One testimony is missing in Chapter 3: Fixed
visual issues on MAC: Fixed
Saves corrupted when watching the credits: Fixed
